WERE CRYING.

1002
01:12:29,440 --> 01:12:34,480
SO HE MADE THEM FOLLOW HIM
THROUGH MANY CHAMBERS

1003
01:12:34,580 --> 01:12:39,310
UNTIL THEY SAW
THE MONSTER'S HEART
SWINGING ABOVE THEM.

1004
01:12:39,420 --> 01:12:42,920
SO COYOTE, WITH HIS STICKS
AND FLINT KNIFE,

1005
01:12:43,020 --> 01:12:44,950
LIT A FIRE.

1006
01:12:45,060 --> 01:12:50,360
